message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product for $170. I think it will be very valuable for you.
I'm interested in the product, but $170 is a bit out of my budget. I'm willing to pay $120.
Thanks for the offer, Bob. I understand your position, but the product is worth more to me than that. Could you do $145?
I'm still interested in the product, but $145 is a bit too high for me. I'm willing to pay $130.
